sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant H as Home (React)
    participant Q as React Query
    participant API as Backend API
    participant G as GitHub (raw fallback)

    U->>H: submit username
    H->>Q: useKanban(username)
    Q->>API: GET /kanban/:username
    API-->>Q: kanban payload
    Q-->>H: cached response
    H->>H: calculate languages/stats
    H->>Board: render columns

    U->>Card: click README
    Card->>H: request openReadme(owner,repo)
    H->>API: GET /readme?owner=&repo=
    API-->>H: raw markdown OR error
    alt if error
      H->>G: try raw.githubusercontent URL(s)
      G-->>H: raw markdown or 404
    end
    H->>ReadmeModal: render markdown
